 MUSTAB SHIRAH\r\n\r\n40) WA WUJOOHUY YAUMA-IZIN 'ALAIHA GHABAR A\r\n\r\n41) TARHAQUHA QATARAH.\r\n\r\n42) ULAA-IKA HUMUL-KAFA RATUL-FAJARAH.", 
